---
title: Louisiana-Style Bacony Red Beans & Rice with Scallions
description: Our chefs brought classic Louisiana flavors to this Black History Month-inspired play on red beans and rice. You'll simmer hearty red beans with bell pepper, scallions, tomato, cumin, and our Cajun Spice Blend until tender, then pile it all over fluffy white rice and finish with a sprinkle of crispy bacon and scallion greens.
